                        <msContents>
                            <summary>Land-donation; chronology</summary>
                            <msItem xml:id="p1_i1">
                                <locus from="2r" to="2v"/>
                                <title>Deed of a land-donation to the Church of the Holy Trinity in Ṣaʿadā ʾAmbā</title>
                                <note>Deed of a donation of land to the benefit of the 
                                    <placeName ref="LOC5427SaedaE">Church of the Holy Trinity in Ṣaʿadā ʾAmbā</placeName>
                                    by <persName ref="PRS4015Fasilada"/> and later by <persName ref="PRS5616IyasuI"/>,
                                    confirmed by <persName ref="PRS9955WaldaMi">rās Walda Mikāʾel</persName> during the reign of
                                    <persName ref="PRS10378Yohanne"/>.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="am">የስላሴ፡ ጉልት፡ ፊት፡ በሐፄ፡ ፋሲል፡ ኋላ፡ በሐፄ፡ ኢያሱ፡ አድያም፡ ሰገድ፡ የተጐለተ፡ ጉልት፡ አድርባ፡ ደቅ፡ ዓንዱ፡ ለመጨሊ፡
                                        </incipit>
                                <textLang mainLang="am"/>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="p1_i2">
                                <locus from="2v" to="6v"/>
                                <title>Chronology from Noah to Yoḥannǝs IV</title>
                                <note>Chronology from Noah to <persName ref="PRS10378Yohanne"/>, possibly calculated according to the
                                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid"/>. The incipit is written in Gǝʿǝz, but the explicit is in
                                    Amharic.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">እስከ፡ ሰማእታት፡ ፪፻፸ወ፯ ሐሰበ፡ ኖኅ፡ ፲፻ወ፯ ወእም፡ ኖኅ፡ እስከ፡ ማየ፡ <pb n="3r"/> አየህ፡ ፯፻ ወእማየ፡ አይህ፡ እስከ፡ 
                                    ሕንፃ፡ ማሃፈድ፡ ፭፻፸፩ ወኮነ፡ ድምሩ፡ ፳፻። ወእምህነፃ፡ ማህፈድ፡ እስከ፡ አብርሐም፡ ፭፻፩ 
                                    ወእምአብር<supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn"></supplied>ሐም፡ እስከ፡ ሙሴ፡ ፬፻፶፭ ወኮነ፡ ድምሩ፡ 
                                    <unclear>፴፻ወ፯፻፶ወ፯</unclear></incipit>
                                <explicit xml:lang="am">ኈልቈ፡ ዓመታት፡ ዘመሳፍንት፡ ታላቅ፡ አሊ፡ ፬ ዓመት። አሊጋዝ፡ ፭ ዓመት፡ የወል<surplus>፡</surplus>ደ፡ ገብርኤል፡
                                    ያሰራት፡ የዋህዱ፡ ፯ ዓመት። የጉግሣ፡ ፳ወ፯ ዓመት። የይማም፡ የማርየ፡ የይራ፡ ፮ ዓመት። የአሊ፡ ፳ወ፪ ዓመት፡ ዘመነ፡ መሳፍንት፡ ፸ወ፩፡ ነው። ዘመን፡ ነገሥታት፡
                                    ቴዎድሮስ፡ ፲፭ ዓመት። ተክለ፡ ጊዮር<choice resp="PRS8999Strelcyn"><sic>ግ</sic><corr>ጊ</corr></choice>ስ፡ ፫ ዓመት።
                                    ዮሐንስ፡ ፲፰ ዓመት።</explicit>
                                <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                            </msItem>
