                            <msItem xml:id="p3_i1">
                                <locus from="34ra" to="38va"/>
                                <title>Deeds of eight land-donations by rās Walda Mikāʾel to the church of the Virgin in Dabra Sinā</title>
                                <note>These are the deeds of eight land donations by <persName ref="PRS9955WaldaMi">rās Walda Mikāʾel</persName>
                                    to the <placeName ref="LOC2377DabraS">Church of Our Lady in Dabra Sinā</placeName> during the reign 
                                    of <persName ref="PRS10378Yohanne"/> and Metropolitan <persName ref="PRS2225Atnatewo"/>, i.e. 
                                    <date notBefore="1872" notAfter="1876">between 1872 and 1876</date>.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ንጽሕፍ፡ ነገረ፡ አጕላት፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ 
                                    ዘ<placeName ref="LOC2377DabraS">ደበረ<supplied reason="undefined">፡</supplied> ሲና፡</placeName> ዘሀለወት፡ 
                                    በምድረ፡ ዛውል፡ ዘወሀባ፡ ክቡር፡ ራስ፡ <persName ref="PRS9955WaldaMi">ወልደ፡ ሚካኤል፡</persName> መፍቀሬ፡ አብያተ፡ ክርስቲያናት፡
                                    ወካህናት፡ ከመ፡ ይኵኖ፡ መርሓ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ወበእንተ፡ ፍቅራ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘተሣየጦ፡ በወርቁ። እምነ፡ አበሊና፡ ወድቀ፡ መሐሬ፡ በ፻ ብር፡
                                    ወምድሩሰ፡ ዘተሣየጦ፡ ምስለ፡ አብ<cb n="34rb"/>ያቲሁ፡ ወማያቲሆሙ፡ ወዕፀዋቲሁ፡</incipit>
                                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            </msItem>
